Name: libplayer
Version: 2.0.1
Release: 1
URL: https://libplayer.geexbox.org/
Source: https://libplayer.geexbox.org/releases/%{name}-%{version}.tar.bz2
License: LGPLv2+
Summary: A multimedia A/V abstraction layer API
Group: System/Libraries
